Introduction

First Bite (Korean: 첫 번째 바이트; Japanese: 最初のバイト) is an American based CO-ED dance/music group that debuted on August 6th 2018. They debuted with the song “Move Over”.

They are based in South Korea and consists of Canaco, Hope, Eddie, Youa and Alexa.
